# Service Standard

This guidance helps teams understand how to apply the [Service Standard](https://www.gov.uk/service-manual) in DfE.

Following the Service Standard ensures you design and build accessible, usable and understandable services for people using DfE services.

This service will enable you to:

- address the different needs of people using DfE services
- navigate the complexities of delivering digital services in the education sector
- meet the Service Standard



